io.github.msdk.datamodel

Interface Feature

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GroupedFeature
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleFeature

    public interface Feature
    A feature represents a single three-dimensional peak in an LC-MS or GC-MS dataset. It must have at least an m/z value and a retention time. In addition, it can contain more detailed data about the peak, such as S/N ratio or raw data points that constitute the feature (Chromatogram).
    Since:
    0.0.8
